data.description: In the heart of Coquille is this centrally located, Move-in Ready home! Enjoy the living room with new Luxury Vinyl plank installed throughout. The kitchen has a very functional layout, features Stainless Steel appliances and has its own pantry. The back-yard is fully fenced and features a nice back deck area. The back-yard is perfect for entertaining or relaxing during the Summer. Call your Realtor and Schedule a showing Today! *See 3D Tour in the link below.*
